### 4.5 `provider_profiles` → Vollständige Spalten-Aufteilung

Die Tabelle `provider_profiles` hat **69 Spalten**. Sie wird aufgeteilt in:
- `provider_profiles` behält **47 Spalten** (Hot Path: Listing, Suche, Buchung, Payment)
- `provider_business_details` erhält **22 Spalten** (Cold Path: Legal, Tax, Onboarding, Finanz)

#### 47 Spalten – BLEIBEN in `provider_profiles`

Diese Spalten werden bei Listings, Suche, Buchungsflow und Stripe täglich abgefragt.

| Spalte                              | Typ             | Warum hier     |
|-------------------------------------|-----------------|----------------|
| `id`                                | UUID PK         | Primärschlüssel |
| `user_id`                           | UUID FK         | → profiles/users |
| `business_name`                     | TEXT NOT NULL   | Listing |
| `business_slug`                     | TEXT?           | URL-Handle |
| `business_description`              | TEXT?           | Listing |
| `short_description`                 | TEXT?           | Listing (Karte) |
| `business_email`                    | TEXT?           | Kontakt |
| `business_email_verified`           | BOOLEAN?        | Verifizierungsstatus |
| `business_email_verification_sent_at` | TIMESTAMPTZ?  | Verifizierung |
| `business_phone_number`             | TEXT?           | Kontakt |
| `business_phone_verified`           | BOOLEAN?        | Verifizierungsstatus |
| `business_is_verified`              | BOOLEAN?        | Admin-Badge |
| `account_is_active`                 | BOOLEAN NOT NULL | Buchungsflow-Guard |
| `can_accept_bookings`               | BOOLEAN NOT NULL | Buchungsflow-Guard |
| `is_profile_complete`               | BOOLEAN?        | Onboarding-Status |
| `has_first_service`                 | BOOLEAN?        | Onboarding-Status |
| `has_payment_method`                | BOOLEAN?        | Payment-Guard |
| `profile_picture_url`               | TEXT?           | Listing |
| `logo_url`                          | TEXT?           | Listing |
| `average_rating`                    | NUMERIC NOT NULL | Listing/Sortierung |
| `total_ratings`                     | INT NOT NULL    | Listing/Sortierung |
| `total_bookings`                    | INT NOT NULL    | Listing/Sortierung |
| `latitude`                          | NUMERIC?        | Geo-Suche |
| `longitude`                         | NUMERIC?        | Geo-Suche |
| `country`                           | TEXT NOT NULL   | Geo |
| `state`                             | TEXT?           | Geo |
| `district`                          | TEXT?           | Geo |
| `location_type`                     | TEXT?           | Listing-Filter |
| `service_area_type`                 | TEXT?           | Listing-Filter |
| `service_cities`                    | TEXT[]?         | Listing-Filter |
| `service_radius_km`                 | NUMERIC?        | Geo-Suche |
| `primary_category_id`               | UUID?           | Listing/Suche |
| `secondary_category_id`             | UUID?           | Listing/Suche |
| `tags`                              | TEXT[]?         | Suche/Filter |
| `working_hours`                     | JSON?           | Verfügbarkeit |
| `cancellation_policy`               | TEXT?           | Buchungsflow |
| `age_restriction`                   | INT?            | Buchungsflow |
| `is_small_business`                 | BOOLEAN NOT NULL | Tax/Payment |
| `financial_access_paused`           | BOOLEAN NOT NULL | Admin-Sperre |
| `onboarding_completed_at`           | TIMESTAMPTZ?    | Onboarding |
| `stripe_account_id`                 | TEXT?           | Payment |
| `stripe_charges_enabled`            | BOOLEAN NOT NULL | Payment-Guard |
| `stripe_payouts_enabled`            | BOOLEAN NOT NULL | Payment-Guard |
| `stripe_verified_user`              | BOOLEAN?        | Payment |
| `stripe_connect_deadline`           | TIMESTAMPTZ?    | Payment |
| `created_at`                        | TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL | — |
| `updated_at`                        | TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL | — |

#### 22 Spalten – ZIEHEN UM nach `provider_business_details`

Diese Spalten werden nur beim Onboarding, in Admin-Views oder vom Steuerberater gebraucht.
Kein einziger Listing- oder Buchungs-Query braucht sie.

| Spalte                         | Typ          | Kategorie         |
|--------------------------------|--------------|-------------------|
| `business_tax_number`          | TEXT?        | Legal / Tax       |
| `business_vat_number`          | TEXT?        | Legal / Tax       |
| `business_court_registration`  | TEXT?        | Legal             |
| `is_business_registered`       | BOOLEAN?     | Legal             |
| `business_type`                | TEXT?        | Legal (enum: `einzelunternehmen` \| `gbr` \| `gmbh` \| `ug` \| `freelancer` \| `other`) |
| `certificates`                 | JSON?        | Legal / Docs      |
| `license_documents`            | JSON?        | Legal / Docs      |
| `impressum`                    | TEXT?        | Legal / Texte     |
| `privacy_policy`               | TEXT?        | Legal / Texte     |
| `terms_conditions`             | TEXT?        | Legal / Texte     |
| `business_street`              | TEXT?        | Geschäftsadresse  |
| `business_house_number`        | TEXT?        | Geschäftsadresse  |
| `business_city`                | TEXT?        | Geschäftsadresse  |
| `business_postal_code`         | TEXT?        | Geschäftsadresse  |
| `address_line2`                | TEXT?        | Geschäftsadresse  |
| `owner_first_name`             | TEXT NOT NULL | Stripe KYC        |
| `owner_last_name`              | TEXT NOT NULL | Stripe KYC        |
| `owner_date_of_birth`          | TEXT?        | Stripe KYC        |
| `accepted_provider_terms_at`   | TIMESTAMPTZ? | Onboarding        |
| `invoice_settings`             | JSON?        | Finanz / Admin    |
| `payout_schedule`              | TEXT?        | Finanz / Admin    |
| `minimum_payout_amount`        | NUMERIC?     | Finanz / Admin    |

**Summe:** 47 + 22 = **69 Spalten** ✓

